      "24": "kai hgagen basileus assuriwn ek babulwnos ton ek counqa kai apo aia kai apo aimaq kai sepfarouain kai katwkisqhsan en polesin samareias anti twn uiwn israhl kai eklhronomhsan thn samareian kai katwkhsan en tais polesin auths",
