      "32": "kai hsan foboumenoi ton kurion kai katwkisan ta bdelugmata autwn en tois oikois twn uyhlwn a epoihsan en samareia eqnos eqnos en polei en h katwkoun en auth kai hsan foboumenoi ton kurion kai epoihsan eautois iereis twn uyhlwn kai epoihsan eautois en oikw twn uyhlwn",
