      "17": "kai apesteilen basileus assuriwn ton qarqan kai ton rafis kai ton rayakhn ek lacis pros ton basilea ezekian en dunamei bareia epi ierousalhm kai anebhsan kai hlqon eis ierousalhm kai esthsan en tw udragwgw ths kolumbhqras ths anw h estin en th odw tou agrou tou gnafews",
