      "23": "outoi kerameis oi katoikountes en nataim kai gadhra meta tou basilews en th basileia autou eniscusan kai katwkhsan ekei",
      "24": "uioi sumewn namouhl kai iamin iarib zare saoul",
      "25": "salem uios autou mabasam uios autou masma uios autou",
