      "21": "kai hcmalwteusan thn aposkeuhn autwn kamhlous pentakiscilias kai probatwn diakosias penthkonta ciliadas onous discilious kai yucas andrwn ekaton ciliadas",
      "22": "oti traumatiai polloi epeson oti para tou qeou o polemos kai katwkhsan ant autwn ews ths metoikesias",
