      "3": "tw idiqwn uioi idiqwn godolia kai souri kai isaia kai semei kai asabia kai mattaqias ex meta ton patera autwn idiqwn en kinura anakrouomenoi exomologhsin kai ainesin tw kuriw",
      "4": "tw aimani uioi aiman boukias kai manqanias kai azarahl kai soubahl kai ierimwq kai ananias kai anani kai hliaqa kai godollaqi kai rwmemqiwd kai iesbakasa kai mallhqi kai wqhri kai meazwq",
