      "10": "kai katwrqwqh h leitourgia kai esthsan oi iereis epi thn stasin autwn kai oi leuitai epi tas diaireseis autwn kata thn entolhn tou basilews",
      "11": "kai equsan to fasec kai prosecean oi iereis to aima ek ceiros autwn kai oi leuitai exedeiran",
