      "16": "kai katwrqwqh kai htoimasqh pasa h leitourgia kuriou en th hmera ekeinh tou poihsai to fasec kai enegkein ta olokautwmata epi to qusiasthrion kuriou kata thn entolhn tou basilews iwsia",
      "17": "kai epoihsan oi uioi israhl oi eureqentes to fasec en tw kairw ekeinw kai thn eorthn twn azumwn epta hmeras",
      "18": "kai ouk egeneto fasec omoion autw en israhl apo hmerwn samouhl tou profhtou kai pantes basileis israhl ouk epoihsan ws to fasec o epoihsen iwsias kai oi iereis kai oi leuitai kai pas iouda kai israhl o eureqeis kai oi katoikountes en ierousalhm tw kuriw",
