      "14": "kai eidon kai anesthn kai eipa pros tous entimous kai pros tous strathgous kai pros tous kataloipous tou laou mh fobhqhte apo proswpou autwn mnhsqhte tou qeou hmwn tou megalou kai foberou kai parataxasqe peri twn adelfwn umwn uiwn umwn kai qugaterwn umwn gunaikwn umwn kai oikwn umwn",
      "15": "kai egeneto hnika hkousan oi ecqroi hmwn oti egnwsqh hmin kai dieskedasen o qeos thn boulhn autwn kai epestreyamen pantes hmeis eis to teicos anhr eis to ergon autou",
      "16": "kai egeneto apo ths hmeras ekeinhs hmisu twn ektetinagmenwn epoioun to ergon kai hmisu autwn anteiconto kai logcai kai qureoi kai ta toxa kai oi qwrakes kai oi arcontes opisw pantos oikou iouda",
