      "15": "en de tw anaplhrousqai ton cronon esqhr ths qugatros aminadab adelfou patros mardocaiou eiselqein pros ton basilea ouden hqethsen wn auth eneteilato o eunoucos o fulax twn gunaikwn hn gar esqhr euriskousa carin para pantwn twn blepontwn authn",
