      "7": "kai epoihsen yhfisma en etei dwdekatw ths basileias artaxerxou kai ebalen klhrous hmeran ex hmeras kai mhna ek mhnos wste apolesai en mia hmera to genos mardocaiou kai epesen o klhros eis thn tessareskaidekathn tou mhnos os estin adar",
      "8": "kai elalhsen pros ton basilea artaxerxhn legwn uparcei eqnos diesparmenon en tois eqnesin en pash th basileia sou oi de nomoi autwn exalloi para panta ta eqnh twn de nomwn tou basilews parakouousin kai ou sumferei tw basilei easai autous",
      "9": "ei dokei tw basilei dogmatisatw apolesai autous kagw diagrayw eis to gazofulakion tou basilews arguriou talanta muria",
