      "12": "kai eklhqhsan oi grammateis tou basilews mhni prwtw th triskaidekath kai egrayan ws epetaxen aman tois strathgois kai tois arcousin kata pasan cwran apo indikhs ews ths aiqiopias tais ekaton eikosi epta cwrais tois te arcousi twn eqnwn kata thn autwn lexin di artaxerxou tou basilews",
      "13": "kai apestalh dia bibliaforwn eis thn artaxerxou basileian afanisai to genos twn ioudaiwn en hmera mia mhnos dwdekatou os estin adar kai diarpasai ta uparconta autwn",
