      "14": "pulas proswpou autou tis anoixei kuklw odontwn autou fobos",
      "15": "ta egkata autou aspides calkeiai sundesmos de autou wsper smiriths liqos",
      "16": "eis tou enos kollwntai pneuma de ou mh dielqh auton",
      "17": "anhr tw adelfw autou proskollhqhsetai sunecontai kai ou mh apospasqwsin",
      "18": "en ptarmw autou epifausketai feggos oi de ofqalmoi autou eidos ewsforou",
      "19": "ek stomatos autou ekporeuontai lampades kaiomenai kai diarriptountai escarai puros",
      "20": "ek mukthrwn autou ekporeuetai kapnos kaminou kaiomenhs puri anqrakwn",
      "21": "h yuch autou anqrakes flox de ek stomatos autou ekporeuetai",
      "22": "en de trachlw autou aulizetai dunamis emprosqen autou trecei apwleia",
      "23": "sarkes de swmatos autou kekollhntai kataceei ep auton ou saleuqhsetai",
      "24": "h kardia autou pephgen ws liqos esthken de wsper akmwn anhlatos",
      "25": "strafentos de autou fobos qhriois tetraposin epi ghs allomenois",
      "26": "ean sunanthswsin autw logcai ouden mh poihswsin doru ephrmenon kai qwraka",
      "27": "hghtai men gar sidhron acura calkon de wsper xulon saqron",
      "28": "ou mh trwsh auton toxon calkeion hghtai men petrobolon corton",
      "29": "ws kalamh elogisqhsan sfurai katagela de seismou purforou",
      "30": "h strwmnh autou obeliskoi oxeis pas de crusos qalasshs up auton wsper phlos amuqhtos",
      "31": "anazei thn abusson wsper calkeion hghtai de thn qalassan wsper exaleiptron",
      "32": "ton de tartaron ths abussou wsper aicmalwton elogisato abusson eis peripaton",
      "33": "ouk estin ouden epi ths ghs omoion autw pepoihmenon egkatapaizesqai upo twn aggelwn mou",
      "34": "pan uyhlon ora autos de basileus pantwn twn en tois udasin"
