      "23": "exeleusetai anqrwpos epi to ergon autou kai epi thn ergasian autou ews esperas",
      "24": "ws emegalunqh ta erga sou kurie panta en sofia epoihsas eplhrwqh h gh ths kthsews sou",
      "25": "auth h qalassa h megalh kai eurucwros ekei erpeta wn ouk estin ariqmos zwa mikra meta megalwn",
      "26": "ekei ploia diaporeuontai drakwn outos on eplasas empaizein autw",
