      "29": "apostreyantos de sou to proswpon taracqhsontai antaneleis to pneuma autwn kai ekleiyousin kai eis ton coun autwn epistreyousin",
      "30": "exaposteleis to pneuma sou kai ktisqhsontai kai anakainieis to proswpon ths ghs",
