      "33": "kai epataxen tas ampelous autwn kai tas sukas autwn kai sunetriyen pan xulon oriou autwn",
      "34": "eipen kai hlqen akris kai broucos ou ouk hn ariqmos",
      "35": "kai katefagen panta ton corton en th gh autwn kai katefagen ton karpon ths ghs autwn",
