      "23": "kai eipen tou exoleqreusai autous ei mh mwushs o eklektos autou esth en th qrausei enwpion autou tou apostreyai thn orghn autou tou mh exoleqreusai",
      "24": "kai exoudenwsan ghn epiqumhthn ouk episteusan tw logw autou",
      "25": "kai egoggusan en tois skhnwmasin autwn ouk eishkousan ths fwnhs kuriou",
