      "21": "exomologhsasqwsan tw kuriw ta eleh autou kai ta qaumasia autou tois uiois twn anqrwpwn",
      "22": "kai qusatwsan qusian ainesews kai exaggeilatwsan ta erga autou en agalliasei",
