      "7": "epistreyon h yuch mou eis thn anapausin sou oti kurios euhrgethsen se",
      "8": "oti exeilato thn yuchn mou ek qanatou tous ofqalmous mou apo dakruwn kai tous podas mou apo olisqhmatos",
      "9": "euaresthsw enantion kuriou en cwra zwntwn",
      "10": "allhlouia episteusa dio elalhsa egw de etapeinwqhn sfodra",
      "11": "egw eipa en th ekstasei mou pas anqrwpos yeusths",
      "12": "ti antapodwsw tw kuriw peri pantwn wn antapedwken moi",
      "13": "pothrion swthriou lhmyomai kai to onoma kuriou epikalesomai",
      "15": "timios enantion kuriou o qanatos twn osiwn autou",
      "16": "w kurie egw doulos sos egw doulos sos kai uios ths paidiskhs sou dierrhxas tous desmous mou",
      "17": "soi qusw qusian ainesews",
      "18": "tas eucas mou tw kuriw apodwsw enantion pantos tou laou autou",
      "19": "en aulais oikou kuriou en mesw sou ierousalhm"
