      "10": "autoi de hpeiqhsan kai parwxunan to pneuma to agion autou kai estrafh autois eis ecqran kai autos epolemhsen autous",
      "11": "kai emnhsqh hmerwn aiwniwn o anabibasas ek ths ghs ton poimena twn probatwn pou estin o qeis en autois to pneuma to agion",
