      "17": "ti eplanhsas hmas kurie apo ths odou sou esklhrunas hmwn tas kardias tou mh fobeisqai se epistreyon dia tous doulous sou dia tas fulas ths klhronomias sou",
      "18": "ina mikron klhronomhswmen tou orous tou agiou sou oi upenantioi hmwn katepathsan to agiasma sou",
