      "4": "kai hxei macaira ep aiguptious kai estai tarach en th aiqiopia kai pesountai tetraumatismenoi en aiguptw kai sumpeseitai auths ta qemelia",
      "5": "persai kai krhtes kai ludoi kai libues kai pantes oi epimiktoi kai twn uiwn ths diaqhkhs mou macaira pesountai en auth",
      "6": "kai pesountai ta antisthrigmata aiguptou kai katabhsetai h ubris ths iscuos auths apo magdwlou ews suhnhs macaira pesountai en auth legei kurios",
